1. On *tera* ovce u štalu. (He drives the sheep into the barn.) 
2. Ja *teram* bicikl uzbrdo. (I pedal my bike uphill.)
3. Oni *teraju* svoje zaposlene da rade prekovremeno. (They make their employees work overtime.)
4. Kako te samo *tera* ta muzika da plešeš? (How does that music make you want to dance?)
5. Šta *tera* tebe da uvek kasniš? (What makes you always run late?)
6. On *tera* svoju decu da uče strane jezike. (He urges his children to learn foreign languages.)
7. Ovaj motor *tera* automobil brzo. (This engine drives the car fast.)
8. Ko *tera* ovu stoku na drum? (Who is driving this cattle on the road?)
9. Ti *teraš* me da se osećam glupo. (You're making me feel foolish.)
10. Ona *terala* je svoje prijatelje da doniraju novac za dobrotvorne svrhe. (She urged her friends to donate money for charity.)